    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a robust double-VANOS system that has been recently serviced for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels via an M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has undergone subframe reinforcement to mitigate common fatigue points, and the suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics. Recent rod bearing replacement ensures internal engine longevity. While showing minor road wear consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains tight and the throttle response is exceptionally linear. A true driver\u2019s car with all critical preventative maintenance addressed.",
